import React from 'react'

import Video from '../../videos/video.mp4'
 const Hero = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <HeroContainer>
    <HeroBg>
        <VideoBg autoPlay loop muted src = {Video} type = 'video/mp4' /> 
    </HeroBg>
    <HeroContent>
        <HeroH1>LIVE MUSIC</HeroH1>
        <HeroH2>EVENTS EVERY DAY</HeroH2>
        <HeroP1>Weekly Lineup</HeroP1>
        <HeroP>SUNDAY - SANDHILL SUNDAY JAM! NEW ACTS WEEKLY & FREE POOL</HeroP>
        <HeroP>MONDAY - OPEN MIC WITH KEVIN CRANE & FREE POOL!</HeroP>
        <HeroP>TUESDAY - TRIVIA & GAME NIGHT WITH LEAH RANTZ!</HeroP>
        <HeroP>WEDNESDAY - KARAOKE WITH SHORTRYDES ENTERTAINMENT!</HeroP>
        <HeroP>THURSDAY - LIVE BLUEGRASS JAM</HeroP>
        <HeroP>FRIDAY - ORIGINAL ARTISTS LIVE!</HeroP>
        <HeroP>SUNDAY - SANDHILL SUNDAY JAM! NEW ACTS WEEKLY & FREE POOL</HeroP>
    </HeroContent>
    </HeroContainer>
    </>
  );
};
export default Hero;
